Add shipping method (Pickup/Delivery) and full admin order editing

Backend:
- ShippingMethod enum on Order + migration (default Delivery)
- CreateOrderDto / OrderDto / new UpdateOrderDto carry shipping method
- OrderService.UpdateAsync rebuilds items and reprices from current catalog
- PUT /api/admin/orders/{id} for full order edit

Frontend:
- Checkout: shipping method selector; Pickup shows store address/hours/phone, Delivery requires address fields
- Admin orders dialog: edit mode toggled by pencil icon to change items, shipping method and address in-place
- Translations (he/en) + store info entries
